---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer - NoticePointBD" description="Disclaimer and content accuracy policy of NoticePointBD.">
  <article class="mx-auto my-8 max-w-3xl rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold">Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      NoticePointBD publishes informational summaries of job circulars, admissions, and results. We are not a government body or official recruiting authority.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
      While we try to keep content accurate and up to date, we cannot guarantee completeness or absolute correctness at all times.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      Users must verify all application details, deadlines, and requirements from official sources before taking action.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
